    "A prompt may simply state a question or task command such as \"Write a haiku about sharks in French.\"",
    "In response, ChatGPT will generate the haiku.",
    "If a haiku about any aspect of sharks is the desired output, then the teacher will have achieved their goal.",
    "However, such general examples are rarely the desired output.",
    "Instead, teachers might want the haiku to be tailored to a specific proficiency level or include specific vocabulary."
